Getting closer to this smoke makes you feel your mental grip on this place slip.

Value.value: You feel the fog of your mind lift as you step through the smoke. You have no idea why you're on the other side of the ruin or how you came by the items or gold.

value.0: You wander into the smoke as your mind clouds with purple and green fog before clearing to reveal a grand, stone city.

Value.value: This large stone depicts the last of this civilization's denizens fleeing to the great pyramid in the center of the Emberwood. You feel confident you'll be able to open the way now.
